\f1\fs22 Elementary 1.5\par
Simple, clean Rainmeter skins.  Elementary currently includes 10 skins:\par
- An analog clock\par
- Date skin (Original and "European" variants)\par
- Time skin (Original and AM/PM variants)\par
- Weather (Celsius and Fahrenheit variants)\par
- System (Linear and stacked variants)\par
- Chronophage (ornamental time-tracking skin)\par
