\b hour \par
\b0 ...is the format code for the Hour in the time skins.  For 12 hour format, use "\b %#I\b0 "; for 24 hour format, use "\b %#H\b0 ".  To add leading zeros, remove the "#" sign (i.e., %I instead of %#I will give you "08" instead of "8").\par
